title Dynamic View: Task Management\nLuồng cập nhật ảnh đại diện lên Cloudinary

actor <<Person>>\nUser as User
participant <<Container>>\nUI as UI
participant <<Container>>\nAPI Gateway as API Gateway
participant <<Container>>\nProfile Service as Profile Service
